4 .c files and 1 .h file is the source code 
makefile is to generate the command 
ReadBestMap is the command program

to generate the ReadBestMap:
input the two command in a GNU environment
make
make clean

Usage for ReadBestMap

./ReadBest db.fa read.fq

db.fa is the genome file , the format is Fasta
read.fq is the read file , the format is Fastq

detail  './ReadBestMap'  for help
